dc_title_s: Totius Lemovici et consinium provinciaru quantum ad dioecesin Lemoviccensen spectant
dc_description_s: 1 map ; 36 x 48 cm|Relief shown pictorially.|Inset: Plan de la ville de Lymoges.|Includes a dedication to Anneto de Levi, Duke of Vantadour, Paris, France and the province of Lemovici.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
